text: (eyata) musa tama janatavata “oba allah vetin udav upakara illa (firavungen obata æti vana duk gæhæta) ivasa dara ganu. niyata vasayenma mema bhumiya allahtama ayitiya!meya tama vahalungen taman adahas karana ayata ayiti kara denu æta. (honda) avasanaya (allahta) biya vannantaya” yayi pævasuveya
